creator: From Now On
descriptionHtml:
The NCAA Volleyball Championship application is your home for this year’s tournament and championship event! Whether you’re on site or following along from home, this app is a must-have for ALL Division I Volleyball fans. With event schedules, social media streams, brackets, and all the scores and stats surrounding the games, the NCAA Volleyball Championship application covers it all!

Features Include:

+ INTERACTIVE BRACKET VIA NCAA.COM– Access the NCAA.com bracket to see results & who your favorite teams will square off against next.

+ SOCIAL STREAM – View real-time twitter feeds within the app on gameday. All your favorite team & NCAA accounts are pulled into our social feed.

+ CHAMPIONSHIP INFO – A home for all the information a fan could need including key times, events, and the need-to-know information to plan your gameday

+ INTERACTIVE STADIUM MAPS – Enhanced location-aware in-venue maps for fans, including amenities such as tailgating and parking, where available

+ SCORES & STATS – All the live scores and stats that fans need and expect during live games

+ NOTIFICATIONS – Custom alert notifications to let fans know everything surrounding Gameday

+ GAMEDAY INFO – In-depth team information, including rosters, quick facts, team & player season stats

+ SPECIAL OFFERS – Receive special updates and offers from the NCAA, including exclusive offers from corporate partners, player and team spotlights, ticket offers, and more!

This NCAA Volleyball Championship app requests the use of location services to provide attendees with additional in-game benefits. Additionally, this app uses notifications to keep you informed of events and offers from the NCAA. You can manage your settings and opt-out of these features at any time.
